item.title: MiniDSP C-DSP 8x12 with Dirac Live Review
item.description: Foreword: While this review is intended to provide insight in to the use and subjective opinion of the end result of the MiniDSP with Dirac Live, it is not intended to be a full tutorial on how to tune with Dirac Live.
